What files do I need?

column1: What should I expect the data format to be?
Each sample in the train and test set has the following information:
• A keyword from that tweet (although this may be blank!)
• The location the tweet was sent from (may also be blank)
You are predicting whether a given tweet is about a real disaster or not. If so, predict a 1. If not, predict a 0.
• sample_submission.csv - a sample submission file in the correct format
• id - a unique identifier for each tweet

column2: - the location the tweet was sent from (may be blank)
- a particular keyword from the tweet (may be blank)

column1: • target - in train.csv only, this denotes whether a tweet is about a real disaster (1) or not (0)
